1. Get just the IP directly:
podman inspect -f '{{ .NetworkSettings.IPAddress }}' <container_id_or_name>

2. If the container is in a user-defined network:
podman inspect -f '{{ .NetworkSettings.Networks.bridge.IPAddress }}' <container_id_or_name>

3. For more details (full JSON output):

podman inspect <container_id_or_name>

